(149, 1, '2016-01-27 18:37:54', '2016-01-27 18:37:54', '[vc_row el_class="spon-sec-1"][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1 class="title-1">MARKETING VIA RETAILWIRE</h1>\r\nWe deliver measurable ROI to our sponsors. RetailWire is designed from the ground up to attract\r\nyour most valuable prospects, educate them and convert them into your customers.\r\n\r\nRetailWire Marketing Program Elements[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class="spon-sec-2"][vc_column][vc_row_inner el_class="box-spon"][vc_column_inner][vc_single_image image="44" img_size="285x130"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1>EMAIL BLASTS</h1>\r\nDirect Email Marketing\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner el_class="box-spon"][vc_column_inner][vc_single_image image="44" img_size="285x130"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1>WEB/SOCIAL PROMO PACKAGE</h1>\r\nA month-long, multi-tiered campaign.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner el_class="box-spon"][vc_column_inner][vc_single_image image="44" img_size="285x130"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1>mPapers Multi-platform</h1>\r\nMulti-platform whitepapers[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner el_class="box-spon"][vc_column_inner][vc_single_image image="44" img_size="285x130"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1>RESEARCH</h1>\r\nCustom, turn-key packages[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner el_class="box-spon last"][vc_column_inner][vc_single_image image="44" img_size="285x130"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1>WEBINARS</h1>\r\nRetailWire-branded Online Seminars[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class="spon-sec-3" css=".vc_custom_1453939406130{margin-top: 40px !important;}"][vc_column width="1/2" el_class="spon-sec-2-l"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p class="text-spo-1">How RetailWire does it...</p>\r\n<p class="text-spo-1">ATTRACTS prospects with the most active,\r\nengaging discussion web site in the retail\r\nindustry;</p>\r\n<p class="text-spo-1">RETAINS them throughout the sponsorship\r\nperiod with relevant content;</p>\r\n<p class="text-spo-1">IDENTIFIES prospects through permission-based response mechanisms;</p>\r\n<p class="text-spo-1">CONVERTS those prospects deemed most\r\nvaluable by delivering them to you for\r\none-on-one engagements.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="text-contact">\r\n<h1>CONTACT US:</h1>\r\nAl McClain\r\n561-627-4974\r\namcclain@retailwire.com\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" el_class="spon-sec-2-r"][contact-form-7 id="162"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Sponsorship', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'sponsorship', '', '', '2016-01-28 00:31:49', '2016-01-28 00:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost/retailwire/?page_id=149', 0, 'page', '', 0),
